  <text>
		  Springs are used in creating <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/transformer" underlined="true">Power Transformers (16A -> 64A)</style>
	and <style color="0xbbffaa">Dynamo Hatches</style>, <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/distillery" underlined="true">Distilleries</style>,
	<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/brewery" underlined="true">Breweries</style>, <style color="0xbbffaa">Blacklights</style> and a few GCyM machines.
  </text>
  <h3>Crafting</h3>
  <text>
	  Springs can be created either manually using two <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/long_rod" underlined="true">Long Rods</style>
	  or in a bender using a single <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/long_rod" underlined="true">Long Rod</style>.
